OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fwindy, with further showers through
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight. Again, some
OL,8,Fof these will be on the heavy side,
OL,9,Fwith the risk of hail.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAnother day of sunny spells
OL,12,Fand scattered showers is expected.
OL,13,FShowers may be a little less frequent
OL,14,Fthen Saturday. Winds remaining brisk,
OL,15,Fthough gradually easing later in the
OL,16,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
